I"Ô<p><strong>How to delete helm tiller from k8s cluster</strong></p>

<p>Sometime, tiller is not working properly in k8s cluster and we want to delete evething Tiller. Tiller has 1 Deployment, 1 ReplicasSet and 1 Pod.</p>

<p>To uninstall tiller from a kubernetes cluster</p>

<pre><code data-trim="" class="yaml">
helm reset
</code></pre>

<p>To delete failed tiller from a kubernetes cluster</p>

<pre><code data-trim="" class="yaml">
helm reset --force
</code></pre>
